N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1155.9 - Accident reports

State Regulations

The operator of any aircraft, watercraft or motor vehicle
involved in any accident causing personal injury, death or property damage at
an air, marine or bus terminal shall report promptly said accident to the
manager. Notes
